social media post made by American skateboarder Nyjah Huston who won a bronze medal at the recently concluded Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999394029405602, \"rank\": 5.2924643861427875e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 446, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nyjah_Huston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nyjah Huston\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nyjah_Huston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nyjah_Huston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huston said the quality of the medals wasn't great after just a week in possession of it.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These Olympic medals look great when they are brand new, but after letting it sit on my skin with some sweat for a little bit \\u2026 they are apparently not as high quality as you would think.\\\"\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American skateboarder, Nyjah Huston who won Bronze at the Paris 2024 Olympics has reservations about the quality of the medal after a week in possession of it.\\ud83d\\ude31\\ud83c\\udfa5@nyjahpic.twitter.com/jT4tYmdb3X  There have been other social media posts, too, about the quality of the medals and earlier this week, Schoeman compared the quality of a few medals in a post on Facebook.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 812, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999394029405602, \"rank\": 5.2924643861427875e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso